ActCanada Foundation for Sustainable Development Technology Act
PrecisAppointment of RONALD KOUDYS of London, Ontario, to be a director of the Canada Foundation for Sustainable Development Technology, to hold office during good behaviour for a term of one year, on a part-time basis, in the place of David Berthiaume.
